    <prj:ScienceGoal mode="Standard">
        <prj:name>Serach for the QPO of the Sgr A*</prj:name>
        <prj:note>We search the periods of QPOs of Sgr A* in band 7 from the light curve of Sgr A*. The relation between the frequency of the QPOs for the first resonance modes and the mass of the GCBH for a given spin parameter is derived. If the periods is known, we can estimate the mass and the spin parameter of the GCBH according to the disk oscillation theory, so the periods is a important clue to know the property of the GCBH. In order to analyze such a periodicity, the successive observation of Sgr A is needed. </prj:note>
